        <briefdescription>
<para>Coefficient table for vertical chroma resampler with 6 taps. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This 3D array contains precomputed filter coefficients used by the vertical chroma resampler for different conversion modes and phases. The coefficients are organized as follows:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>First dimension: Conversion type (e.g., 422-&gt;420, 420-&gt;422)</para></listitem><listitem><para>Second dimension: Phase of the resampling process</para></listitem><listitem><para>Third dimension: Tap coefficients for the filter (6 taps per phase)</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para>The coefficients are used to perform chroma resampling between different chroma subsampling formats.</para><para><simplesect kind="see"><para>XV_VCRSMPLR_NUM_CONVERSIONS </para><simplesectsep/><para>XV_VCRSMPLR_MAX_PHASES </para><simplesectsep/><para>XV_VCRSMPLR_TAPS_6 </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
